类 GenericGroovyXmlContextLoader

    ContextLoader, SmartContextLoader

    public class GenericGroovyXmlContextLoader
extends GenericXmlContextLoader
    Concrete implementation of AbstractGenericContextLoader that reads bean definitions from Groovy scripts and XML configuration files.

    Default resource locations are detected using the suffixes "-context.xml" and "Context.groovy".

    从以下版本开始:
    4.1
    作者:
    Sam Brannen
    另请参阅:
    GroovyBeanDefinitionReader, GenericXmlContextLoader, AnnotationConfigContextLoader
